Package cams.posts.post_entities

Class Message

java.lang.Object
cams.posts.post_entities.Message
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
Direct Known Subclasses:
Approval, Enquiry, Reply, Suggestion
public abstract class Message extends Object implements Serializable
Represents an abstract base class serving as a template for types of messages. Objects of this type are Serializable. Provides basic structure for messages with functionality to set and display content.
